Well today is the day we finally put all the pieces of the mission together. We're suppose to meet in the SECURITY CENTER back at E.I. this morning. The Doctor is introducing me to his security chief today as well and I get to finally work in my new lab!

&lt;So, big day try not to fuck it up.....&gt;

"Man since I been wearing this ring I've been getting so much rest..... I gonna have to look into this vibranium....." You mumble to yourself.
